The Western banner is a reward from completing the Western Provinces Diary. There are four depending on which tier of the diary is completed:

  • Western banner 1, from the easy tasks
  • Western banner 2, from the medium tasks
  • Western banner 3, from the hard tasks
  • Western banner 4, from the elite tasks
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.

rawContent:
The '''Western banner''' is a reward from completing the [[Western Provinces Diary]]. There are four depending on which tier of the diary is completed:

*[[Western banner 1]], from the easy tasks
*[[Western banner 2]], from the medium tasks
*[[Western banner 3]], from the hard tasks
*[[Western banner 4]], from the elite tasks
